  </header>
  <div class = "gridWrapper">
    <section>
      <div class = "primary">
        <p>The Artemis program is a robotic and human Moon exploration program.<br><br> 
        Artemis is led by NASA & partnered with the European, Canadian & Japanese space agencies.<br><br> 
        The program's long-term goal is to <span class = "emphasis">establish a permanent base camp on the Moon and facilitate human missions to Mars.</span></p>
      </div>
    </section> 
