        Unlike the other program components, the Human Landing System is to be commercially developed by private industries<br><br>
        The contract was awarded to SpaceX in July 2021 for an initial $2.89bn, modified in Nov 2022 by an additional $1.15bn.<br><br>
        SpaceX intends to use a variant of their <span class = "link"><a href = "/page5">Starship spacecraft</a></span> for this purpose.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
